text: Eamon Farren (born May 19, 1985) is an Australian actor. His first well known role was as Richard Horne in the 2017 revival of Twin Peaks. He would go on to have roles in Winchester (2018) and appeared in the series The ABC Murders (2018) and The Witcher (2019â€“present).
